odase

Class ModelAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.ModelAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HedwigModel, Model, ModelReadOnly, ModelUpdate, SwrlModel, ValidatableModel

    public abstract class ModelAdaptor
extends Object
implements Model
    This class implements most of the odase.Model methods in terms of other methods. To get a fully working instance of Model, the following methods need to be implemented:
    • query
    • queryAsserted
    • addObjectPropertyValue
    • removeObjectPropertyValue
    • addDatatypePropertyValue
    • removeDatatypePropertyValue
    • remove
    • rename
    • validate
